  <Lines>k__BackingField:
  - <Npc>k__BackingField: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 668c08530be223b44883e3880f11ee48, type: 2}
    <Expression>k__BackingField: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 15a032d1f64921b49a6cec6c0a26887d, type: 2}
    <Text>k__BackingField:
    - Bon matin.
  - <Npc>k__BackingField: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 668c08530be223b44883e3880f11ee48, type: 2}
    <Expression>k__BackingField: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 3d35d0e1530830e42b12a5e80d0329dc, type: 2}
    <Text>k__BackingField:
    - "Ce matin, quand j\u2019\xE9tais dans la calle, j\u2019ai aper\xE7u des rats. "
  - <Npc>k__BackingField: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 668c08530be223b44883e3880f11ee48, type: 2}
    <Expression>k__BackingField: {fileID: 11400000, guid: f0358eca1d351f540a61dc689202b2b8, type: 2}
    <Text>k__BackingField:
    - "Un signe d\u2019une mauvaise hygi\xE8ne si vous voulez mon avis."
  - <Npc>k__BackingField: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 668c08530be223b44883e3880f11ee48, type: 2}
    <Expression>k__BackingField: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 3d35d0e1530830e42b12a5e80d0329dc, type: 2}
    <Text>k__BackingField:
    - "Mais bon, il faut s\u2019occuper de r\xE9gler \xE7a avant que \xE7a cause
      des probl\xE8mes."
